# Recommended .gitignore for this workspace

### Node / JavaScript
**/node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnp-debug.log

### Logs
logs/
*.log

### Build / Output
dist/
build/
out/
lib/
*.tsbuildinfo

### TypeScript
*.tsbuildinfo

### VS Code - ignore user-specific VSCode files but keep launch/tasks/etc needed for F5
.vscode/*
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json

### Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

### Coverage
coverage/
.nyc_output/

### OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

### Editors
*.swp
*~
.idea/
*.iml

### Compiled outputs / source maps (if your build emits them)
**/out/**/*.js
**/out/**/*.js.map

### Misc
.cache/
/*.log
